title: Laurie Anderson Complete Studio Album Discography
description:
The complete studio album discography of Laurie Anderson, as mentioned on her official website at www.laurieanderson.com. Most of them are 320 kbs.

It includes the following albums:

Laurie Anderson - 1981 - You're the Guy I Want to Share My Money With
Laurie Anderson - 1982 - Big Science
Laurie Anderson - 1984 - Mister Heartbreak
Laurie Anderson - 1984 - United States Live
Laurie Anderson - 1986 - Home Of The Brave
Laurie Anderson - 1989 - Strange Angels
Laurie Anderson - 1994 - Bright Red
Laurie Anderson - 1995 - The Ugly One With the Jewels and Other Stories
Laurie Anderson - 2001 - Life on a String
Laurie Anderson - 2001 - Live in New York
Laurie Anderson - 2010 - Homeland

The only one not included on her website is Talk Normal, which is a compilation album, repeating songs already included elsewhere.

Enjoy all this avant-garde artist has to offer in music!
